# LLM API Configuration
# Choose ONE provider and set its API key below

# ============================================
# OPTION 0: Google Generative AI (Gemini)
# ============================================
# Sign up: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# Free: Generous free tier (unlimited requests within rate limit)
# Cost: Free tier is sufficient for this use case
# HOW TO GET KEY:
# 1. Go to https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
# 2. Click "Create API Key in new project"
# 3. Copy the API Key
# 4. Set below:
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=your-google-api-key-here
VITE_LLM_PROVIDER=google

# ============================================
# OPTION 1: OpenAI (Recommended for Quality)
# ============================================
# Sign up: https://platform.openai.com/signup
# Free: $5 trial credit (expires in 3 months)
# Cost: ~$0.00015 per request (700+ free requests)
# Uncomment below to use OpenAI:
# VITE_OPENAI_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here
# VITE_LLM_PROVIDER=openai

# ============================================
# OPTION 2: Groq (Free & Fast - No CC Required)
# ============================================
# Sign up: https://console.groq.com
# Free: Unlimited (rate-limited but no cost)
# Uncomment below and set VITE_LLM_PROVIDER to use Groq
# VITE_GROQ_KEY=gsk-your-groq-api-key-here
# VITE_LLM_PROVIDER=groq

# ============================================
# OPTION 3: Hugging Face (Open Source Models)
# ============================================
# Sign up: https://huggingface.co
# Free: Rate-limited free tier
# Uncomment below and set VITE_LLM_PROVIDER to use Hugging Face
# VITE_HF_KEY=hf_your-huggingface-token-here
# VITE_LLM_PROVIDER=huggingface

# ============================================
# OPTION 4: Together AI (Free Tier Available)
# ============================================
# Sign up: https://www.together.ai
# Free: Generous free tier
# Uncomment below and set VITE_LLM_PROVIDER to use Together AI
# VITE_TOGETHER_KEY=your-together-api-key-here
# VITE_LLM_PROVIDER=together

# ============================================
# NOTES
# ============================================
# - Only set ONE provider's credentials above
# - VITE_LLM_PROVIDER specifies which to use (optional, auto-detects if only one key set)
# - If no keys are set, the app uses a local fallback message
# - NEVER commit this file with real API keys to git!
# - On Vercel, add these as Environment Variables in Project Settings
